# Valentines Day Card - 2010

This is the code for my AVR driven Valentines Card.

More information is available at: http://www.tony.thompson.name/2010/02/valentines-card/
Pictures of the final product are available at: http://www.flickr.com/photos/tonious/sets/72157623325815567/

## Files and Demos

blink.c - Demonstrates a chaser
eh.c - Displays the capital letter 'A'.
alphabet.c - Displays the lower case 
stdiotest.c - Demonstrates the use of I/O stream functions.
buttontest.c - Displays a '*' when the button is pressed.
sleeptest.c - Demonstrates sleep mode.
valcard.c - The final card.

font.h - A CBM inspired font.
ledmatrix.c,.h - The LED matrix driver.

## Installation

Any demo can be installed via:

make flash_<demoname>; make fuse

For example, the 'eh' demo can be installed via:

make flash_eh; make fuse

